data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. SELLERS MOTIVATED!!! Welcome home! Built by Casa Fresca in 2021, this spacious 2-story, 5-bedroom Catalina floorplan is perfectly situated on a corner lot on a peaceful street within the vibrant community of Riverstone. With its modern features, spacious layout, desirable location, and access to a multitude of amenities, this house and community make a wonderful opportunity for you to call this place your new home. This exceptional property offers many desirable features and amenities that will leave you feeling captivated. As soon as you turn onto the street, you will immediately be amazed at the location. As one of the most desirable and larger lots in the community, this allows plenty of room for outdoor activities and entertainment. As you walk through the front door, you are greeted by a long hallway that leads to an open-concept living and dining area. The kitchen boasts modern appliances, ample counter space, a large kitchen island with gorgeous quartz countertops, and a large walk-in pantry. As you cook or are enjoying a meal in the dining area, you will appreciate the sliding doors that lead out to the spacious fully fenced backyard, which is the perfect place to entertain family and friends. The swing set is also included in the sale if you would like it! Additionally, the main floor features a den, which can be used for multiple purposes, such as a secondary living space or a home office. Ascending the staircase, you will discover the luxurious primary bedroom, complete with a private ensuite bathroom featuring a double sink vanity and a HUGE walk-in closet. One other spacious bedroom is located on the main floor, and three other generously sized bedrooms are located on the upper floor. All provide ample space for family members or guests, each offering their own unique comfort and charm. There is also a massive recreation room on the upper floor that can be used for anything you could imagine: a play room, movie room, office, game room - the possibilities are endless! Walking down the hallway on the upper floor, you will be amazed when you see the the laundry room, which features ample storage areas. This vast and well-organized area is equipped with stunning cabinetry, making it the perfect space for all your laundry needs. The cabinetry is not only functional but also adds a touch of elegance to this room. Other awesome features of this home include: smart home features, walk-in closets, water filtration system, water softener, ceiling fans, and an in wall pest system.  The Riverstone community boasts an abundance of amenities that include playgrounds, scenic walking trails around lakes and ponds, a clubhouse, dog park, and TWO sparkling pools. This beautiful house is waiting for you to make wonderful new memories here. Call today to make this house your HOME!
